        "subject": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize error messages in lfs_ladvise()",
        "message": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize error messages in lfs_ladvise()\n\nError messages in lfs_ladvise() and the llapi functions it calls\nare updated to a standard format.  Messages are prefixed with\nthe name of the utility and the command that caused the error.\nUser-provided values are delimited with single quotes.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Steve Guminski <stephenx.guminski@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Iab4c64a361ca3d4178939929a665108b8da6a5f6\n"
